 />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">天水圍 反申請&middot;不停跑</span><br />\n時間 ： 2030<br />\n地點 ：李東海小學 校門<br />\n*一日未完 一日都要跑 訓練打側跑<br />\n<br />\n=====================<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">111全城連儂日</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月11日 星期六<br />\n時間 ： 有待公佈<br />\n地點 ：九龍 : 尖東 旺角 黃大仙 長沙灣<br />\n新界 : 元朗 青衣 荃灣 大埔 葵芳 沙田 馬鞍山 將軍澳<br />\n港島 : 金鐘 銅鑼灣 炮台山 西灣河<br />\n<br />\n===============<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2020 港共受刑 天下制裁 遊行前集氣大會</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月12日 星期日<br />\n時間 ： 1500-1700<br />\n地點 ：愛丁堡廣場<br />\n(*不反對通知書申請中)"},{"pid":"56ca15b370a31e497afc52628b1141b033084440","tid":1817324,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13245ea469d3e4b9d3f2af5a954fd2aea2228070","tid":1817324,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c1c534ef328fc3c1984d11c03f25930e711c54b0","tid":1817324,"uid":188279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"626a07fc92d3f8e7f0e32890cc1282aab2a2f17a","tid":1817324,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd18dfd2dfb71c084c78d6ceb822f082cd3230f1","tid":1817324,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"黃屍啱啱訓醒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"和理非不嬲都平行時空緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1962597bb67ee0092ac9edd79ab141d43582ddd5","tid":1817324,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得早幾個月 藍絲係狗面前用摺登打人頭 啲狗都係當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"